## Global Color Palette — "Nomina Deep"

All colors are defined as CSS custom properties in `globals.css`.

### Primary (Royal Purple)
- `--primary`: `#6C5CE7` — Primary buttons, active nav, links, focus rings
- `--primary-hover`: `#5A4BD1` — Button/link hover state
- `--primary-light`: `#EDE9FE` — Selected backgrounds, light badges, active tabs
- `--primary-foreground`: `#FFFFFF` — Text on primary backgrounds

### Secondary (Emerald)
- `--secondary`: `#00B894` — Success states, positive actions, green badges
- `--secondary-hover`: `#00A37D` — Hover state
- `--secondary-light`: `#D1FAE5` — Light success backgrounds

### Accent (Rose)
- `--accent`: `#FD79A8` — Attention items, special CTAs, notifications
- `--accent-light`: `#FDE8EF` — Light accent backgrounds

### Neutrals
- `--background`: `#FAFAFA` — Page background
- `--surface`: `#FFFFFF` — Cards, panels, modals, dropdowns
- `--surface-hover`: `#F5F3FF` — Hover state for cards and rows
- `--border`: `#E5E7EB` — Borders, dividers, separators
- `--border-strong`: `#D1D5DB` — Stronger borders (focused inputs)

### Text
- `--text-primary`: `#1F2937` — Headings, body text, primary content
- `--text-secondary`: `#6B7280` — Subtitles, labels, secondary content
- `--text-muted`: `#9CA3AF` — Placeholders, disabled, captions
- `--text-on-primary`: `#FFFFFF` — Text on primary/secondary colored backgrounds

### Semantic
- `--destructive`: `#EF4444` — Delete buttons, error text, error borders
- `--destructive-hover`: `#DC2626` — Delete hover
- `--destructive-light`: `#FEE2E2` — Error backgrounds
- `--warning`: `#F59E0B` — Warning badges, caution notices
- `--warning-light`: `#FEF3C7` — Warning backgrounds
- `--info`: `#3B82F6` — Info badges
- `--info-light`: `#DBEAFE` — Info backgrounds

