## Typography Tokens

- **Font family:** `Geist` (sans-serif body), `Geist Mono` (monospace/code) — already configured in layout.tsx
- **Headings:** Use `font-semibold` or `font-bold` with `leading-tight` (1.25)
  - Page title: `text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold`
  - Section title: `text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold`
  - Card title: `text-lg font-semibold`
  - Subsection: `text-base font-medium`
- **Body:** `text-sm` (14px) as default body size with `leading-relaxed` (1.625)
- **Emphasis:** `text-base` (16px) for important body text
- **Small:** `text-xs` (12px) for badges, timestamps, helper text
- **Color pairings:** Headings use `--text-primary`, body uses `--text-secondary`, muted uses `--text-muted`

---

## Spacing Tokens

- **Page-level padding:** `px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`
- **Content max width:** `max-w-6xl mx-auto`
- **Section vertical spacing:** `py-6 sm:py-8`
- **Card padding:** `p-4 sm:p-6`
- **Card gap (grids):** `gap-4 sm:gap-6`
- **Form field spacing:** `space-y-4`
- **Inline element gap:** `gap-2` (small), `gap-3` (medium), `gap-4` (large)

---

## Border, Radius & Shadow Tokens

### Border Radius
- Cards & panels: `rounded-xl`
- Buttons & inputs: `rounded-lg`
- Badges & chips: `rounded-full`
- Avatars: `rounded-full`
- Modals: `rounded-2xl`

### Shadows
- Cards (resting): `shadow-sm`
- Cards (hovered): `shadow-md`
- Modals & dropdowns: `shadow-lg`
- Popovers: `shadow-xl`

### Borders
- Default: `border border-[var(--border)]`
- Focused inputs: `ring-2 ring-[var(--primary)] border-[var(--primary)]`
- Error inputs: `border-[var(--destructive)] ring-2 ring-[var(--destructive)]`

---

## State Styles

### Buttons
```
Default:    bg-[var(--primary)] text-white rounded-lg
Hover:      bg-[var(--primary-hover)]
Focus:      ring-2 ring-offset-2 ring-[var(--primary)]
Disabled:   opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed
```

### Cards
```
Default:    bg-[var(--surface)] border border-[var(--border)] rounded-xl shadow-sm
Hover:      shadow-md bg-[var(--surface-hover)] transition-all duration-200
```

### Inputs
```
Default:    bg-[var(--surface)] border border-[var(--border)] rounded-lg text-sm
Focus:      border-[var(--primary)] ring-2 ring-[var(--primary)]/20
Error:      border-[var(--destructive)] ring-2 ring-[var(--destructive)]/20
Placeholder: text-[var(--text-muted)]
```

---

## Dos
- ✅ Use CSS custom properties for all colors
- ✅ Use responsive Tailwind prefixes on every layout
- ✅ Include `transition-all duration-200` on interactive elements
- ✅ Use `focus-visible:` for keyboard focus styles
- ✅ Test all pages at 375px, 768px, and 1440px

## Don'ts
- ❌ Never use hardcoded hex colors like `text-[#333]` — use tokens
- ❌ Never use fixed pixel widths for layouts (e.g., `w-[800px]`)
- ❌ Never skip hover/focus states on clickable elements
- ❌ Never use `hidden` without a responsive counterpart (e.g., `hidden sm:block`)
- ❌ Never create a desktop-only layout without mobile consideration
